195
00:18:02,000 --> 00:18:06,050
Ya-Ya-Ya... Yak San. My name is Yak San.

196
00:18:06,050 --> 00:18:10,940
 Just how... How did this happen? 

197
00:18:10,940 --> 00:18:18,680
So on the seventh day of the month, you secretly infiltrated General Lee Seong Gye's house

198
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:22,190
