202
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:36,840
That girl didn't personally say it, but

203
00:18:36,840 --> 00:18:39,620
I've also lived my life on the ground for thirty years.

204
00:18:39,620 --> 00:18:42,420
There's no doubt that she's from Hwa Sa Dan.

205
00:18:43,810 --> 00:18:46,640
